                  double usualDose,
                  boolean inducesTinnitus)
        Full Constructor
        Parameters:
        name - - name of the medication
        genericName - - generic name of the medication
        dose - - total amount of medication prescribed over the duration (mg)
        duration - - duration of how long the medication is to be taken for
        chemicalCategory - - description of the chemical category
        action - - function of the drug in various body systems
        application - - description of how the medication is to be applied
        usualDose - - dose of one application (mg)
        inducesTinnitus - - boolean for whether or not the medication induces tinnitus
